POISED API Testing Strategy
=========================
1>Parameter->We checked with diffrent values and sometime also give blank
2>Output->
3>interop->Date format fod diffrent country
4>Securiy->check all authirization issues
5>Errors->heck the errors are coming correctly or not
6>Data->ex After creating data check data is avilabe or not,check the response time by serching data in database

(POISED)



